    "text": [
        "Dear Professor Kin,",
        "I hope this letter finds you well. I am writing this letter to reach out for help from you regarding a reference letter.",
        "I am applying for a position as senior financial management in a famous accounting firm currently. This is a job that I have been being passionate about since I was studying at university. As you may know, I have gotten my CPA licence, so I quit my previous work as an assistant accountant in a factory which I was extremely sick of.",
        "According to the job description, apart from helping clients manage their super accounts, there are countless client-based tasks involved in it which is my  weakness, so I genuinely want to be accepted by this company.",
        "One of the requirements of this job application is to provide a reference letter from your former tutor. There are several points that should be covered in this letter, including my personality, academic performance in college and enthusiasm towards tough work.",
        "I would be awfully grateful if you could write this reference letter for me. If you would like to discuss this reference letter further, I would be delighted to come to your office. Please let me know whether it is convenient for you to write this letter at the earliest opportunity. I am looking forward to your reply.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Nina Guan"
